			<div class="content" id="post-content-3904865">
									

<p>An experiment with brevity and ambiguity.</p>
<p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1533814092" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;">The Great Hippo</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1533814092" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;">Captain Kirby</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1533814092" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Taffeta</a></span> for looking this over.</p>
<p>In case clarity is needed, &quot;the man&quot; is Researcher Conwell, and &quot;his colleague&quot; is Researcher Ferro.</p>
<p>That's right, its a <a href="/those-twisted-pines-hub">Those Twisted Pines</a> tale.</p>
<p>Enjoy the read.</p>
<p><em>JC</em></p>

